(939, 119, 'services_repeater_0_services_repeater_content', 'We offer a sustainable solution for Iowa trees by reclaiming discarded lumber and transforming them into beautiful wood slabs. With a focus on preserving the health of the urban forest, our dedicated team ensures that these trees find a second life as stunning and eco-friendly materials. Whether you\'re in need of unique wood slabs or standard lumber, we provide a wide selection of premium products that showcase the natural beauty of reclaimed wood.'),
