(1175, 124, 'about_content', 'TreeHugger II is a company focused on repurposing locally sourced material from TreeHugger Complete Tree Care.(Link to our Website)  Our crew is there for each step of the process, from removal to revival because we believe that in the right hands there can be a second life for your tree. It is an important TreeHugger Crew value that makes both of our companies unique.'),
