(1769, 177, 'services_repeater_0_services_repeater_content', 'We offer a sustainable solution for Iowa trees by reclaiming discarded lumber and transforming them into beautiful wood slabs. With a focus on preserving the health of the urban forest, our dedicated team ensures that these trees find a second life as stunning and eco-friendly materials. Whether you\'re in need of unique wood slabs or standard lumber, we provide a wide selection of premium products that showcase the natural beauty of reclaimed wood.'),
(1770, 177, '_services_repeater_0_services_repeater_content', 'field_64f6dbcea2540'),
(1771, 177, 'services_repeater_1_services_repeater_title', 'iDRY Vacuum Kiln Drying'),
(1772, 177, '_services_repeater_1_services_repeater_title', 'field_64f6dba9a253f'),
(1773, 177, 'services_repeater_1_services_repeater_content', 'iDRY Vacuum Kiln Drying offers a highly effective method for drying wood by creating a low-pressure (vacuum) environment. This process prevents damage or darkening of the wood while promoting the development of vibrant colors. With its advanced technology, iDRY Vacuum Kiln Drying reduces the boiling point of water, allowing for efficient and precise moisture removal, resulting in high-quality, dry wood ready for various applications.'),
(1774, 177, '_services_repeater_1_services_repeater_content', 'field_64f6dbcea2540'),
(1775, 177, 'services_repeater_2_services_repeater_title', 'Custom Milling and Flattening '),
(1776, 177, '_services_repeater_2_services_repeater_title', 'field_64f6dba9a253f'),
(1777, 177, 'services_repeater_2_services_repeater_content', 'With our Lucas mill, we can cut large logs into unique slab dimensions, providing a rare find for special projects. Coupled with the IDRY Plus Kiln, we create an ideal partnership to transform Central Iowa\'s oldest trees into cherished heirloom pieces. Additionally, we offer flattening services to eliminate warping and twists in your slabs, ensuring a straight and production-ready outcome.'),
(1778, 177, '_services_repeater_2_services_repeater_content', 'field_64f6dbcea2540'),
(1779, 177, 'services_repeater_3_services_repeater_title', 'Log Transportation'),
(1780, 177, '_services_repeater_3_services_repeater_title', 'field_64f6dba9a253f'),
(1781, 177, 'services_repeater_3_services_repeater_content', 'Are you in need of delivery assistance? We are here to lend a hand. Our fleet of equipment is ready to transport your wood to the mill and kiln, ensuring a seamless process from start to finish.'),
(1782, 177, '_services_repeater_3_services_repeater_content', 'field_64f6dbcea2540'),
(1783, 177, 'services_repeater_4_services_repeater_title', 'Tree Removal'),
(1784, 177, '_services_repeater_4_services_repeater_title', 'field_64f6dba9a253f'),
(1785, 177, 'services_repeater_4_services_repeater_content', 'TreeHugger utilizes specialized equipment and our expertise to provide tree removal services for any tree, any size, any location. Whether due to storm damage, disease, or your preference, we are here to remove your tree for a clean finish.'),
